    "description": "Mahindra Navistar International Enterprises invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Visakhapatnam location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Mahindra Navistar International Enterprises:\nMahindra Navistar International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mahindra Navistar International Enterprises!",
